name: 苹果十二生肖剪纸拟我表情 Apple designed Zodiac Chinese Paper-cutting Style Memoji (Community)
description:
This is a remix based on kylin deng's sharing.


The paper-cutting style memoji SVG vectors from Apple’s wallpapers designed for 2022 Chinese New Year are added to this file.


该文档基于 kylin deng 的分享。


从苹果为2022中国新年设计的十二生肖剪纸风格拟我表情的壁纸中，转换而来的SVG矢量图被添加进这个文档。
